#~ msgctxt "body.e35f585f-23e2-4c2e-81a7-ca2b4de21aee.items.24355ed7-0c4b-4136-b95e-41815b4dcec9.description"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "<i>From Plural Reality (Japan):</i> Inspired by democratic challenges in Otoineppu, a Japanese village facing population decline, <a id=\"a1\">this tool helps residents understand and express their "
#~ "views</a> before participating in community deliberation."
